channel.title: Looking for some help
channel.description:
Hello, I'm Miles. I'm looking for someone who is fluent in Java and computer basics who wants to help me create an RS2 Server. I'm slowly learning on my own when I have the free time, I'm more into the RSC Scene but it seems RS2 is a huge industry.
If you are willing to help me / work with me, just add my msn; watkins-@live.com or PM me. Thanks.
